* Monitor Sharing Activity\nthrough Audit Logs
** Captured events
***_ createShare, createRecipient
***_ grantOnShare, revokeOnShare
***_ Recipient data access
** Audit queries
***_ service_name = 'unityCatalog'
***_ Track share/recipient creation
***_ Monitor recipient data access
** Key fields
***_ action_name
***_ request_params.recipient_name
***_ request_params.share_name
***_ user_identity.email
** Use cases
***_ Compliance reporting
***_ Unauthorized access detection
***_ Sharing activity dashboards
